snippet.title: Sole Collector
snippet.description: Sole Collector's official YouTube channel features exclusive content detailing everything in the world of sneakers, featuring exclusive interviews with all of the industry's top designers, insiders and signature athletes in the game. Want more? Be sure to head on over to http://www.SoleCollector.com
